import React from 'react'; import { BarChart3, CheckCircle, XCircle, MinusCircle, Trophy, TrendingUp } from 'lucide-react'; const ScoreSummary = ({ scores }) => { const totalScored = scores.length; const goodMatches = scores.filter(s => s.score === 'good').length; const averageMatches = scores.filter(s => s.score === 'average').length; const badMatches = scores.filter(s => s.score === 'bad').length; const getPercentage = (count) => { return totalScored > 0 ? ((count / totalScored) * 100).toFixed(1) : 0; }; const getTopScore = () => { if (scores.length === 0) return null; return scores.reduce((top, current) => current.font.score > top.font.score ? current : top ); }; const topScore = getTopScore(); return (

Scoring Summary

Real-time evaluation statistics

Good Matches
{goodMatches}
{getPercentage(goodMatches)}%
Average Matches
{averageMatches}
{getPercentage(averageMatches)}%
Bad Matches
{badMatches}
{getPercentage(badMatches)}%
{/* Top Score Highlight */} {topScore && (
Highest Scoring Font
{topScore.font.family_name}
Score: {topScore.font.score.toFixed(1)}
{topScore.font.conversion.toLocaleString()}
)} {/* Overall Stats */}
Total Fonts Scored {totalScored}
Success Rate {getPercentage(goodMatches)}%
); }; export default ScoreSummary;
